text: Ðis is þara feower hyda boc æt Wiþiglea þe eadwig cyng gæbocode ælfwoldæ his þegnæ on ece yrfæ.
Ðis synd þa land ge mere to Wiþiglea ærest of lulles beorge andlang burnan to cynulfes treowe þonon suþ on þerpaþ to megstanes dene þonon on Wiþigleageat.

Of þam geate to seg broce þonon on ucing cumb þonon andlang weges to wyddan beorge þonon on wiþig sled andlang sledes on gericte to þam smalan wege andlang weges on gerihte to brocenan beorge þonon eft on lulles beorge.
